page.title: 16sport
page.content: In autumn right through to spring i play {rugger} at newbold R.F.C. We usualy play every sunday. Last season we played 6 matches. That may not seem a lot but it is condsidering we did'nt start till December. We only won two matches out of the six matches and next season we are hoping for more matches. In 1985 i went to see Coventry versus Aston villa it was a good afternoon. Just before half time Withe scored his first goal. In the second half Withe scored again and { Walters scored. At full time it was Aston villa 3 Coventry 0. In the 1985 Embasy World Snooker Championships i went to see the match between Alex Higgins and Terry Griffiths. We went because my uncle lived in sheffield. In the end Terry Griffiths won.
